      "label": "Fig. 2",
      "caption": "<p class=\"caption-description\" data-placeholder-text=\"Caption...\" contenteditable=\"true\">Time series of the model inputs at the different plots used for model simulations (N13, S16, S19 and S22): soil water potential (<i>ψ</i><sub>soil</sub>, black dashed lines), nighttime trunk water potential (<i>ψ</i><sub>trunk</sub>) of larch (red) and spruce (blue) and nighttime air temperature (<i>T</i><sub>air</sub>, grey). Periods used for model simulations (i.e. from DOY 80 to 300) are denoted by a white background.</p>",
