    {
      "_id": "MPParagraphElement:E7157BE4-C959-4058-8A83-01757A7CF080",
      "contents": "<p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"MPParagraphElement:E7157BE4-C959-4058-8A83-01757A7CF080\" class=\"MPElement\" data-object-type=\"MPParagraphElement\">The genotype of <i>DβH</i> 5’-Ins/Del was identified by the same method as reported in our previous study. Two independent investigators who were blinded to the clinical information of subjects confirmed the genotype of this polymorphism. If the assignments of genotype that they confirmed were inconsistent, these samples would further be repeated (see <span class=\"cross-reference\" data-reference-id=\"MPAuxiliaryObjectReference:92EF91A2-4ACE-4719-839C-DA32A3E45591\"><span class=\"kind elementIndex\"><b>Figure 3</b></span></span>).</p>",
