      "_id": "MPParagraphElement:00CFC79C-504D-4A24-978A-DD38ACF39927",
      "contents": "<p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"MPParagraphElement:00CFC79C-504D-4A24-978A-DD38ACF39927\" class=\"MPElement\" data-object-type=\"MPParagraphElement\">This sample had 0.78-0.99 statistical power to detect this polymorphism associated with suicide attempts in chronic schizophrenia through three models, with a genetic effect of 2.0 (a=0.05, two-tailed test).</p>",
      "createdAt": 1689589036,
      "sessionID": "579459a9-d137-4b7f-8996-db10bd057ae5",
      "updatedAt": 1689589036,
      "_revisions": {
