      "_id": "MPParagraphElement:07CF6387-03FB-462F-BEF3-34FEFDECC4EA",
      "contents": "<p xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" id=\"MPParagraphElement:07CF6387-03FB-462F-BEF3-34FEFDECC4EA\" class=\"MPElement\" data-object-type=\"MPParagraphElement\">We should like to thank Dr. Da Chun Chen, Zhi Ren Wang, Jia Li, Song Chen, and Gui Gang Yang for all of their hark work and significant contributions toward this work.</p>",
      "createdAt": 1689589036,
      "sessionID": "579459a9-d137-4b7f-8996-db10bd057ae5",
      "updatedAt": 1689589036,
      "_revisions": {
